---

<section
  id="doctor"
  class="py-24 bg-primary text-white overflow-hidden relative"
>
  <!-- Decorative background elements -->
  <div
    class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/2 h-full bg-slate-800/20 -skew-x-12 translate-x-24"
  >
  </div>
  <div
    class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-64 h-64 bg-accent/5 rounded-full blur-[100px] -ml-32 -mb-32"
  >
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-20">
      <!-- Doctor Image Area -->
      <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2">
        <div class="relative max-w-lg mx-auto">
          <!-- Artistic Frame -->
          <div
            class="aspect-[4/5] bg-slate-800 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-[0_30px_60px_-15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] border border-white/5 relative group"
          >
            <img
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1612349317150-e413f6a5b16d?q=80&w=1000&auto=format&fit=crop"
              alt="Op. Dr. İsim Soyisim"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale-[10%] group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700 group-hover:scale-105"
            />
            <div
              class="absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-32 bg-gradient-to-t from-primary/80 to-transparent"
            >
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Floating Experience Badge -->
          <div
            class="absolute -bottom-8 -right-8 bg-accent text-primary p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl hidden md:block animate-pulse-slow"
          >
            <span class="block text-4xl font-serif font-bold leading-none"
              >15+</span
            >
            <span
              class="block text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mt-2 opacity-80"
              >Yıllık Tecrübe</span
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Doctor Bio Content -->
      <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 space-y-8">
        <div>
          <span
            class="text-accent uppercase text-sm font-bold tracking-[0.3em] block mb-4"
            >Uzman Görüşü</span
          >
          <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-serif leading-[1.1] mb-6">
            Op. Dr. <span class="italic text-accent">İsim Soyisim</span>
          </h2>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-gray-400">
            <span class="w-12 h-px bg-accent/50"></span>
            <span class="text-lg font-light tracking-wide italic"
              >Estetik ve Plastik Cerrahi Uzmanı</span
            >
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-gray-300 font-light text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Sanat ve bilimin kesiştiği noktada, her hastamız için özel olarak
          tasarlanmış estetik çözümler sunuyoruz. Burun estetiğinde (Rinoplasti)
          doğallığı ve fonksiyonelliği ön planda tutan yaklaşımımızla, sadece
          burnunuzu değil, yaşam kalitenizi de iyileştiriyoruz.
        </p>

        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-10 pt-4">
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <h4 class="text-white font-serif text-xl">Uzmanlık Alanları</h4>
            <ul class="text-gray-400 space-y-2 text-sm font-light">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent"></span> Piezo Rinoplasti
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent"></span> Revizyon
                Cerrahisi
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent"></span> Yüz Germe
                (Facelift)
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <h4 class="text-white font-serif text-xl">Uluslararası Başarı</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 font-light leading-relaxed">
              EBOPRAS & TPRECD onaylı uzmanlığımızla uluslararası standartlarda
              cerrahi deneyim.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="pt-10 flex items-end justify-between">
          <img
            src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/fa/Signature_sample.svg"
            alt="Signature"
            class="h-16 opacity-40 filter invert contrast-125"
          />
          <a
            href="#contact"
            class="text-accent border-b border-accent/30 hover:border-accent transition-colors pb-1 text-sm tracking-widest uppercase font-bold"
            >RANDEVU AL</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
